3 or more Level 6 monstersThis card gains 1000 ATK for each Xyz Material attached to it. If this card attacks, at the end of the Damage Step: You can detach 1 Xyz Material from this card; this card can attack an opponent's monster again in a row. At the end of the Battle Phase: You can pay half your Life Points, then target 2 cards in any Graveyard(s); place 1 of them on top of the Deck, and if you do, attach the other to this card as an Xyz Material.
